x w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="140">Ja — <strong data-start="5" data-end="14">genau</strong>, du hast das richtig verstanden 👍<br data-start="49" data-end="52">
Bei <strong data-start="56" data-end="97"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Adjust</span></span></strong> hat jede App <strong data-start="111" data-end="139">App Token + Event Tokens</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="142" data-end="165">Hier kurz klar erklärt:</p>
<hr data-start="167" data-end="170">
<h2 data-section-id="zxcjx3" data-start="172" data-end="201">🔑 1. App Token (apptoken)</h2>
<ul data-start="202" data-end="329">
<li data-section-id="xw6p32" data-start="202" data-end="237">
<p data-start="204" data-end="237">Das ist die <strong data-start="216" data-end="237">ID der ganzen App</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xvwdbw" data-start="238" data-end="289">
<p data-start="240" data-end="289">Jede App in Adjust hat <strong data-start="263" data-end="289">einen festen App Token</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11nyy6" data-start="290" data-end="329">
<p data-start="292" data-end="329">Wird im Tracking-Link benutzt, z. B.:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="330" data-end="370"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>https://app.adjust.com/APP_TOKEN</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="372" data-end="426">👉 Bedeutet: “Diese Installation gehört zu dieser App”</p>
<hr data-start="428" data-end="431">
<h2 data-section-id="cql95p" data-start="433" data-end="453">🎯 2. Event Token</h2>
<ul data-start="454" data-end="687">
<li data-section-id="mxdzfd" data-start="454" data-end="547">
<p data-start="456" data-end="547">Jeder <strong data-start="462" data-end="478">In-App Event</strong> hat einen eigenen Token<br data-start="502" data-end="505">
(z. B. signup, purchase, level_complete)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12ss0ht" data-start="548" data-end="640">
<p data-start="550" data-end="640">Wird erstellt, wenn du ein Event in Adjust anlegst <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 79px;"><a href="https://help.adjust.com/en/article/basic-event-setup?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://help.adjust.com/en/article/basic-event-setup?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 79px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">help.adjust.com</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vm9i3g" data-start="641" data-end="687">
<p data-start="643" data-end="687">Ist eine <strong data-start="652" data-end="687">feste ID für genau dieses Event</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="689" data-end="701">👉 Beispiel:</p>
<ul data-start="702" data-end="743">
<li data-section-id="17o4gd8" data-start="702" data-end="721">
<p data-start="704" data-end="721">signup → <code data-start="713" data-end="721">abc123</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6il1ss" data-start="722" data-end="743">
<p data-start="724" data-end="743">purchase → <code data-start="735" data-end="743">xyz789</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="745" data-end="748">
<h2 data-section-id="m33ji4" data-start="750" data-end="799">🔗 3. Kombination (wichtig für Games / Offers)</h2>
<p data-start="800" data-end="844">Bei Tracking oder Callback sieht das so aus:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="8nm7v" data-start="846" data-end="879">Event tracking (S2S Beispiel)</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="880" data-end="955"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>https://s2s.adjust.com/event?event_token=abc123&amp;app_token=APP_TOKEN</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="vtfba" data-start="957" data-end="979">Callback Parameter</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="980" data-end="1041"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>event_callback_abc123=https://yourserver.com/postback</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1042" data-end="1130">→ Event Token wird direkt im Parameter verwendet <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 79px;"><a href="https://help.adjust.com/en/article/event-callbacks-partner?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://help.adjust.com/en/article/event-callbacks-partner?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 79px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">help.adjust.com</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<hr data-start="1132" data-end="1135">
<h2 data-section-id="1i9ux6j" data-start="1137" data-end="1163">🧠 Wichtig zu verstehen</h2>
<ul data-start="1164" data-end="1237">
<li data-section-id="xxpn1a" data-start="1164" data-end="1192">
<p data-start="1166" data-end="1192"><strong data-start="1166" data-end="1192">App Token = welche App</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9wf6i1" data-start="1193" data-end="1237">
<p data-start="1195" data-end="1237"><strong data-start="1195" data-end="1237">Event Token = was der User gemacht hat</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1239" data-end="1243">Und:</p>
<ul data-start="1244" data-end="1385">
<li data-section-id="lzout6" data-start="1244" data-end="1345">
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1345">Event Tokens sind <strong data-start="1264" data-end="1285">fix und eindeutig</strong> (ändern sich nicht) <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 79px;"><a href="https://help.adjust.com/en/article/event-callbacks?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://help.adjust.com/en/article/event-callbacks?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 79px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">help.adjust.com</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="azoroe" data-start="1346" data-end="1385">
<p data-start="1348" data-end="1385">Namen können sich ändern, Token nicht</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1387" data-end="1390">
<h2 data-section-id="166i4ga" data-start="1392" data-end="1434">💡 Bezug zu “Adjust Games / Offerwalls”</h2>
<p data-start="1435" data-end="1472">Bei Games (z. B. ZBD, Freecash etc.):</p>
<ul data-start="1473" data-end="1627">
<li data-section-id="1xc5fxm" data-start="1473" data-end="1532">
<p data-start="1475" data-end="1532">Offers nutzen <strong data-start="1489" data-end="1505">Event Tokens</strong>, um Fortschritt zu tracken</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xse6km" data-start="1533" data-end="1627">
<p data-start="1535" data-end="1544">Beispiel:</p>
<ul data-start="1547" data-end="1627">
<li data-section-id="bc20cd" data-start="1547" data-end="1570">
<p data-start="1549" data-end="1570">Install → automatisch</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1q6z7an" data-start="1573" data-end="1598">
<p data-start="1575" data-end="1598">Level 5 → Event Token A</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="npq7s4" data-start="1601" data-end="1627">
<p data-start="1603" data-end="1627">Purchase → Event Token B</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1629" data-end="1632">
<p data-start="1634" data-end="1779">Wenn du willst, kann ich dir <span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">zeigen, wie man aus einem Adjust-Link <strong data-start="38" data-end="75" data-is-last-node="" node="[object Object]" class="group-hover:entity-accent">AppToken + EventTokens extrahiert</strong></span></span> oder <span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">automatisch umwandelt</span></span> (passt zu deinem Callback-Usecase).</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center