f1-2" data-testid="conversation-turn-6" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a9f633ef-b072-471a-bab7-e6d743cf01fb" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="71">Ja 👍 ich kenne die App — und du liegst auch richtig mit deinem Gefühl:</p>
<p data-start="73" data-end="188">👉 <strong data-start="76" data-end="188"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">JustPlay</span></span> ist sehr wahrscheinlich ein klassisches Adjust-/Offerwall-Game-System.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="190" data-end="193">
<h2 data-section-id="hncbw6" data-start="195" data-end="228">🧠 Was JustPlay eigentlich ist</h2>
<ul data-start="229" data-end="479">
<li data-section-id="1qyhq28" data-start="229" data-end="296">
<p data-start="231" data-end="296">Eine <strong data-start="236" data-end="256">Play-to-earn App</strong> → du spielst Games und bekommst Coins</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3d8nkx" data-start="297" data-end="389">
<p data-start="299" data-end="389">Coins werden alle paar Stunden in Geld umgewandelt <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 98px;"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?gl=US&amp;hl=en&amp;id=com.justplay.app&amp;utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?gl=US&amp;hl=en&amp;id=com.justplay.app&amp;utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 98px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Google Play</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="161yuoi" data-start="390" data-end="479">
<p data-start="392" data-end="479">Auszahlung z. B. über <strong data-start="414" data-end="439">PayPal oder Giftcards</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 83px;"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?gl=US&amp;hl=en&amp;id=com.justplay.app&amp;utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?gl=US&amp;hl=en&amp;id=com.justplay.app&amp;utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 83px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Google Play</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="481" data-end="492">👉 Wichtig:</p>
<ul data-start="493" data-end="611">
<li data-section-id="1opkdn1" data-start="493" data-end="611">
<p data-start="495" data-end="558">Du wirst <strong data-start="504" data-end="535">nicht für das Spiel bezahlt</strong>, sondern indirekt für:</p>
<ul data-start="561" data-end="611">
<li data-section-id="1o4gam" data-start="561" data-end="566">
<p data-start="563" data-end="566">Ads</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5pikus" data-start="569" data-end="584">
<p data-start="571" data-end="584">Game installs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1z4hds" data-start="587" data-end="611">
<p data-start="589" data-end="611">Engagement (Retention)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="613" data-end="616">
<h2 data-section-id="1xlbilk" data-start="618" data-end="668">🔗 Warum das ein “Adjust Game” ist (dein Punkt)</h2>
<p data-start="669" data-end="727">Auch wenn sie es nicht offen sagen, technisch läuft es so:</p>
<ul data-start="729" data-end="830">
<li data-section-id="1emkkb3" data-start="729" data-end="830">
<p data-start="731" data-end="753">JustPlay arbeitet mit:</p>
<ul data-start="756" data-end="830">
<li data-section-id="5rcqqc" data-start="756" data-end="788">
<p data-start="758" data-end="788"><strong data-start="758" data-end="788">Offerwalls / Game Partnern</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i9fod" data-start="791" data-end="830">
<p data-start="793" data-end="830"><strong data-start="793" data-end="830">Tracking (Adjust, AppsFlyer etc.)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="832" data-end="850">👉 Typischer Flow:</p>
<ol data-start="851" data-end="1061">
<li data-section-id="1hblw5l" data-start="851" data-end="894">
<p data-start="854" data-end="894">Du installierst ein Spiel aus JustPlay</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qnx6yf" data-start="895" data-end="929">
<p data-start="898" data-end="929">Spiel hat <strong data-start="908" data-end="927">Adjust SDK drin</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1v53xrg" data-start="930" data-end="1004">
<p data-start="933" data-end="956">Events werden getrackt:</p>
<ul data-start="960" data-end="1004">
<li data-section-id="24ue4p" data-start="960" data-end="969">
<p data-start="962" data-end="969">install</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pv5y1u" data-start="973" data-end="988">
<p data-start="975" data-end="988">level reached</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jwhznn" data-start="992" data-end="1004">
<p data-start="994" data-end="1004">purchase</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xzknvb" data-start="1005" data-end="1061">
<p data-start="1008" data-end="1061">JustPlay bekommt Geld → gibt dir einen kleinen Anteil</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1063" data-end="1066">
<h2 data-section-id="1rdj29b" data-start="1068" data-end="1122">🎯 Bezug zu AppToken + EventToken (das du meintest)</h2>
<p data-start="1123" data-end="1152">Genau hier passt dein Wissen:</p>
<ul data-start="1154" data-end="1250">
<li data-section-id="w7012e" data-start="1154" data-end="1191">
<p data-start="1156" data-end="1191">jedes Spiel = eigener <strong data-start="1178" data-end="1191">App Token</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19cwb8c" data-start="1192" data-end="1250">
<p data-start="1194" data-end="1250">Fortschritt = <strong data-start="1208" data-end="1224">Event Tokens</strong> (z. B. level 5, level 10)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1252" data-end="1271">👉 Beispiel intern:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1272" data-end="1354"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>install → automatisch</span><br><span>level_5 → event_token_abc</span><br><span>purchase → event_token_xyz</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1356" data-end="1379">JustPlay nutzt das, um:</p>
<ul data-start="1380" data-end="1459">
<li data-section-id="19whdcq" data-start="1380" data-end="1422">
<p data-start="1382" data-end="1422">zu prüfen ob du wirklich gespielt hast</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vmmotu" data-start="1423" data-end="1459">
<p data-start="1425" data-end="1459">auszuzahlen / Coins zu berechnen</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1461" data-end="1464">
<h2 data-section-id="q27wj7" data-start="1466" data-end="1490">⚠️ Realität (wichtig)</h2>
<p data-start="1491" data-end="1514">Auch wenn es legit ist:</p>
<ul data-start="1516" data-end="1697">
<li data-section-id="826nzd" data-start="1516" data-end="1617">
<p data-start="1518" data-end="1617">Einnahmen kommen hauptsächlich von <strong data-start="1553" data-end="1577">Ads + Tracking Deals</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 81px;"><a href="https://www.earnologist.com/justplay-review-earning-guide-is-it-legit/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.earnologist.com/justplay-review-earning-guide-is-it-legit/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 81px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Earnologist</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="czrheg" data-start="1618" data-end="1659">
<p data-start="1620" data-end="1659">Coin → Cash ist <strong data-start="1636" data-end="1657">nicht transparent</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hgcswk" data-start="1660" data-end="1697">
<p data-start="1662" data-end="1697">Einnahmen sind meist <strong data-start="1683" data-end="1697">sehr klein</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1699" data-end="1729">👉 echte User sagen oft sowas:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1730" data-end="1813">
<p data-start="1732" data-end="1813">~“0.10–1€ pro Session” (stark schwankend) <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 60px;"><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/JustPlay/comments/1sjpt9a/how_do_you_earn_on_this_app_efficiently/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.reddit.com/r/JustPlay/comments/1sjpt9a/how_do_you_earn_on_this_app_efficiently/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 60px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Reddit</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1815" data-end="1818">
<h2 data-section-id="17od2ng" data-start="1820" data-end="1837">💡 Kurz gesagt</h2>
<ul data-start="1838" data-end="2004">
<li data-section-id="nipjaa" data-start="1838" data-end="1865">
<p data-start="1840" data-end="1865">✅ Ja, JustPlay ist real</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lctem0" data-start="1866" data-end="1930">
<p data-start="1868" data-end="1930">✅ Ja, es nutzt sehr wahrscheinlich <strong data-start="1903" data-end="1928">Adjust/Event Tracking</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ytva6t" data-start="1931" data-end="2004">
<p data-start="1933" data-end="2004">❗ Aber: es ist eher ein <strong data-start="1957" data-end="1976">Ad/Offer-System</strong>, kein echtes “Game earning”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2006" data-end="2009">
<p data-start="2011" data-end="2122">Wenn du willst, kann ich dir zeigen, <strong data-start="2048" data-end="2089"><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">wie man bei JustPlay/ähnlichen Apps die Adjust-Links + Event Tokens ausliest</span></span></strong> (das ist genau dein Bereich 👀).</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center