<h2 data-section-id="1byu86q" data-start="1574" data-end="1604">🧠 Real reason this happens</h2>
<p data-start="1605" data-end="1630">The image I generated is:</p>
<ul data-start="1631" data-end="1687">
<li data-section-id="12k18aw" data-start="1631" data-end="1655">
<p data-start="1633" data-end="1655">cinematic (wide depth)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xoaqdt" data-start="1656" data-end="1687">
<p data-start="1658" data-end="1687">designed like a <strong data-start="1674" data-end="1687">wallpaper</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1689" data-end="1755">But your site needs:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="1713" data-end="1737">“texture background”</strong>, not “hero image”</p>
