f="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼn">*</span><span> {</span><br><span>    margin: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    box-sizing: </span><span class="ͼq">border-box</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">body</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-family: </span><span class="ͼq">ui-sans-serif</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">system-ui</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">Arial</span><span>;</span><br><span>    color: #fff;</span><br><br><span>    background:</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.8</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.95</span><span>)),</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼq">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"backround.png"</span><span>);</span><br><br><span>    background-size: </span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>    background-position: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    background-repeat: </span><span class="ͼq">no-repeat</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* ✅ FIXED BANNER */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-banner</span><span> {</span><br><span>    position: </span><span class="ͼq">relative</span><span>;</span><br><span>    width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    height: </span><span class="ͼq">260</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    overflow: </span><span class="ͼq">hidden</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* better image handling */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-banner</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">img</span><span> {</span><br><span>    width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    height: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    object-fit: </span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl">/* 🔥 keeps hunter visible */</span><br><span>    object-position: </span><span class="ͼq">right</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    filter: </span><span class="ͼn">brightness</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0.55</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* ✅ SMOOTH BLEND INTO BACKGROUND */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-banner</span><span>::</span><span class="ͼs">after</span><span> {</span><br><span>    content: </span><span class="ͼr">""</span><span>;</span><br><span>    position: </span><span class="ͼq">absolute</span><span>;</span><br><span>    bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    left: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    height: </span><span class="ͼq">120</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼn">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼq">to</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">bottom</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.95</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><br><span>    );</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* overlay */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-overlay</span><span> {</span><br><span>    position: </span><span class="ͼq">absolute</span><span>;</span><br><span>    top: </span><span class="ͼq">50</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    left: </span><span class="ͼq">80</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    transform: </span><span class="ͼn">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">-50</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>);</span><br><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.2</span><span>);</span><br><span>    backdrop-filter: </span><span class="ͼn">blur</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>);</span><br><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">30</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">12</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    border: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">140</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.25</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* text */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-overlay</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h1</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">64</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-weight: </span><span class="ͼq">800</span><span>;</span><br><span>    letter-spacing: </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    font-family: </span><span class="ͼr">'Arial Black'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">sans-serif</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼn">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">90</span><span class="ͼn">deg</span><span>, #b6ff5c, #6aff00, #b6ff5c);</span><br><span>    background-size: </span><span class="ͼq">200</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    -webkit-background-clip: </span><span class="ͼq">text</span><span>;</span><br><span>    -webkit-text-fill-color: </span><span class="ͼq">transparent</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    animation: </span><span class="ͼq">shine</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">6</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">linear</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">infinite</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    text-shadow:</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">140</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.7</span><span>),</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.4</span><span>),</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">40</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">80</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.2</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">@keyframes</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">shine</span><span> {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span> { background-position: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>; }</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span> { background-position: </span><span class="ͼq">200</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>; }</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-overlay</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">p</span><span> {</span><br><span>    margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    color: #ccc;</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">18</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* content */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">container</span><span> {</span><br><span>    max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">1400</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin: </span><span class="ͼq">auto</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">40</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* search */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">search</span><span> {</span><br><span>    margin: </span><span class="ͼq">30</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">flex</span><span>;</span><br><span>    gap: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">search</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">input</span><span> {</span><br><span>    flex: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">14</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">22</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">32</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">.85</span><span>);</span><br><span>    border: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">180</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">120</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">.15</span><span>);</span><br><span>    color: #fff;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* cards */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">cards</span><span> {</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">grid</span><span>;</span><br><span>    grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼn">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">auto-fit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼn">minmax</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">240</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>));</span><br><span>    gap: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">card</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">22</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">32</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">.85</span><span>);</span><br><span>    border: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">180</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">120</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">.1</span><span>);</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">16</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    text-align: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    transition: </span><span class="ͼq">.2</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span>;</span><br><span>    backdrop-filter: </span><span class="ͼn">blur</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">6</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">card</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>    transform: </span><span class="ͼn">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">-5</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>);</span><br><span>    border-color: </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">180</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">120</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">.4</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">logo</span><span> {</span><br><span>    width: </span><span class="ͼq">84</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    height: </span><span class="ͼq">84</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* button */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">btn</span><span> {</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">inline-block</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼn">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">180</span><span class="ͼn">deg</span><span>, #c8f07a, #9ec94e);</span><br><span>    color: #111;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">16</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    text-decoration: </span><span class="ͼq">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-weight: </span><span class="ͼq">bold</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">footer</span><span> {</span><br><span>    text-align: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    color: #777;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">40</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* 📱 MOBILE FIX */</span><br><span class="ͼn">@media</span><span> (max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">768</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>) {</span><br><span>    .</span><span class="ͼs">hero-banner</span><span> {</span><br><span>        height: </span><span class="ͼq">200</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    }</span><br><br><span>    .</span><span class="ͼs">hero-overlay</span><span> {</span><br><span>        left: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>        padding: </span><span class="ͼq">15</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    }</span><br><br><span>    .</span><span class="ͼs">hero-overlay</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h1</span><span> {</span><br><span>        font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">40</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>}</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/style&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3953" data-end="3956">
<h2 data-section-id="v061ws" data-start="3958" data-end="3990">💡 WHY THIS WORKS (important)</h2>
<ul data-start="3991" data-end="4202">
<li data-section-id="ro6onw" data-start="3991" data-end="4047">
<p data-start="3993" data-end="4047"><code data-start="3993" data-end="4024">object-position: right center</code> → keeps hunter visible</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11ua2d1" data-start="4048" data-end="4104">
<p data-start="4050" data-end="4104">removed <code data-start="4058" data-end="4088">background-attachment: fixed</code> → no weird zoom</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1agll6m" data-start="4105" data-end="4160">
<p data-start="4107" data-end="4160">gradient fade → blends banner into background cleanly</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1w1t0t" data-start="4161" data-end="4202">
<p data-start="4163" data-end="4202">responsive fix → doesn’t break on phone</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4204" data-end="4207">
<h2 data-section-id="qm2l3x" data-start="4209" data-end="4244">⚠️ ONE THING YOU SHOULD STILL DO</h2>
<p data-start="4245" data-end="4304">Your background image is still a bit “too detailed” for UI.</p>
