<hr data-start="6233" data-end="6236">
<h3 data-section-id="126m5a2" data-start="6238" data-end="6277">What actually got fixed (important)</h3>
<ul data-start="6278" data-end="6549">
<li data-section-id="1k9ni8u" data-start="6278" data-end="6333">
<p data-start="6280" data-end="6333">❌ <code data-start="6282" data-end="6305">background-size: 120%</code> → caused zoom → <strong data-start="6322" data-end="6333">removed</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n6qbmu" data-start="6334" data-end="6376">
<p data-start="6336" data-end="6376">❌ banner too tall → <strong data-start="6356" data-end="6376">reduced to 200px</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e0fbne" data-start="6377" data-end="6436">
<p data-start="6379" data-end="6436">❌ random cropping → <strong data-start="6399" data-end="6436">controlled with <code data-start="6417" data-end="6434">object-position</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4vzwxo" data-start="6437" data-end="6496">
<p data-start="6439" data-end="6496">❌ logos stretching → <strong data-start="6460" data-end="6496">fixed with <code data-start="6473" data-end="6494">object-fit: contain</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="k8vc3g" data-start="6497" data-end="6549">
<p data-start="6499" data-end="6549">❌ overlay floating weird → <strong data-start="6526" data-end="6549">centered vertically</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
