<p data-start="45" data-end="57">👉 You want:</p>
<ul data-start="58" data-end="124">
<li data-section-id="1ohqnrr" data-start="58" data-end="82">
<p data-start="60" data-end="82">FULL image visible ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x5qcav" data-start="83" data-end="100">
<p data-start="85" data-end="100">NOT cropped ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15v6hzp" data-start="101" data-end="124">
<p data-start="103" data-end="124">BUT also NOT huge ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="126" data-end="206">So the correct solution is:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="157" data-end="177">limit the height</strong>, while still using <code data-start="197" data-end="206">contain</code></p>
<hr data-start="208" data-end="211">
<h2 data-section-id="4q64d0" data-start="213" data-end="230">✅ THE REAL FIX</h2>
<p data-start="232" data-end="240">We keep:</p>
<ul data-start="241" data-end="278">
<li data-section-id="13wwvtr" data-start="241" data-end="278">
<p data-start="243" data-end="278"><code data-start="243" data-end="264">object-fit: contain</code> (no cropping)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="280" data-end="288">And add:</p>
<ul data-start="289" data-end="335">
<li data-section-id="1r5qjuf" data-start="289" data-end="335">
<p data-start="291" data-end="335"><code data-start="291" data-end="303">max-height</code> → controls size without cutting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="337" data-end="340">
<h2 data-section-id="1ll7nzo" data-start="342" data-end="370">🔥 REPLACE ONLY THIS PART</h2>
<p data-start="372" data-end="417">Change your <code data-start="384" data-end="398">.hero-banner</code> and <code data-start="403" data-end="408">img</code> to this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="419" data-end="855"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-banner</span><span> {</span><br><span>    position: </span><span class="ͼq">relative</span><span>;</span><br><span>    width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    height: </span><span class="ͼq">220</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>; </span><span class="ͼl">/* 👈 controls banner size */</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">flex</span><span>;</span><br><span>    justify-content: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    align-items: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    overflow: </span><span class="ͼq">hidden</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">180</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">120</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">.15</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-banner</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">img</span><span> {</span><br><span>    max-height: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;   </span><span class="ͼl">/* 👈 keeps it inside */</span><br><span>    max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    object-fit: </span><span class="ͼq">contain</span><span>; </span><span class="ͼl">/* 👈 no cropping EVER */</span><br><span>    filter: </span><span class="ͼn">brightness</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0.6</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div 