<hr data-start="857" data-end="860">
<h2 data-section-id="n02r54" data-start="862" data-end="882">💡 What this does</h2>
<ul data-start="884" data-end="1015">
<li data-section-id="1x0pvux" data-start="884" data-end="923">
<p data-start="886" data-end="923">Image scales <strong data-start="899" data-end="907">down</strong> to fit height</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y1ricc" data-start="924" data-end="950">
<p data-start="926" data-end="950">Keeps full proportions</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="u9fw9" data-start="951" data-end="974">
<p data-start="953" data-end="974">NEVER cuts anything</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wwj9pt" data-start="975" data-end="1015">
<p data-start="977" data-end="1015">Banner size stays clean + controlled</p>
</li>
</ul>
