<p data-start="4206" data-end="4259">make hunter slightly zoomed but still fully visible</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yavh4a" data-start="4260" data-end="4303">
<p data-start="4262" data-end="4303">add fade into background (blend effect)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q9lzr3" data-start="4304" data-end="4332">
<p data-start="4306" data-end="4332">or animate banner subtly</p>
</li>
</ul>
